    <bridgehead id='apostrophe'>Apostrophe</bridgehead>

  <para>Besides the usual latin letters (some used in digraphs), the
  Yanesha&#x02BC; orthography uses an apostrophe to write a glotal
  stop. This is best represented using U+02BC &#x02BC; MODIFIER
  LETTER APOSTROPHE.</para>

